# Nuvia Logo & Favicon Update

I have generated a new, awesome logo for Nuvia that matches the iridescent, premium aesthetic of your heuristic intelligence platform.

## The New Logo
The design features a 3D iridescent torus with holographic gradients, symbolizing fluidity and intelligence.

![Nuvia New Logo](file:///C:/Users/Vastaare/.gemini/antigravity/brain/67afe1a7-4744-4ffa-a097-975390ec16e7/nuvia_logo_v2_1776660103930.png)

## Changes Made
- **Logo Generation**: Created a high-fidelity image based on the existing color palette (teals, blues, and purples).
- **ICO Conversion**: Converted the logo into a multi-resolution `favicon.ico` (16x16 up to 64x64).
- **Deployment**: Replaced the existing favicon at `frontend/app/favicon.ico`.

> [!TIP]
> You may need to hard-refresh your browser (Ctrl+F5) to see the new favicon in your local development environment.
